{"tid":1315792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「即時」軍政府強烈譴責暴力示威者","createTime":"2019-07-14T14:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:35:04.000Z","uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"037f41a729396571bad27f03b616429fc5b2272b","tid":1315792,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"政府強烈譴責暴力示威者<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（七月十四日）表示，下午和平示威遊行結束後，有部分示威者故意堵塞道路，以暴力襲擊警察，並肆意破壞社會安寧。政府對這些違法行為，予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n　　法治是香港的基石，社會絕不容忍這些暴力行為。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月14日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時38分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/14/P2019071400959.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F14%2FP2019071400959.htm&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP979ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e406009b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/14/P2019071400959.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd777a36e489a06db1edc00497d9de2fb93844be","tid":1315792,"uid":230621,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"農曆七月都未到就見鬼衝擊，痴撚線<br />\n我淨係見到黑警衝擊囉。"},{"pid":"56ceda948f416fd06238c135c09284810372c922","tid":1315792,"uid":33307,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"分化撚出現（軍政府）<br />\n<br />\n下午<span style=\"color: red;\">和平</span>示威遊行結束後，有<span style=\"color: red;\">部分示威</span>者故意堵塞道路，以暴力襲擊警察，並肆意破壞社會安寧。"},{"pid":"d20dd3383cc63088986d459aca07dd341f807213","tid":1315792,"uid":75664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"唔講入新城市開無雙？？"},{"pid":"087e834e9d2f608b57328bd6f689467f1eb01faf","tid":1315792,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"入侵私人地方呢?"},{"pid":"416f2f470f042bf9f9c99ba55210436c2a5e682a","tid":1315792,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d20dd3383cc63088986d459aca07dd341f807213","tid":13